Text.val: Jumps to the proper field. This needs to be manually set due to different visible conditions on controls
Otherwise, when moving between the lines of different var types, the focus jumps from a 'From' var to a 'To' var.

ExpSyntax.val: 'Range cannot be defined on the same field twice.'

CtrlGoto( CASE({0,16},'A','AlpUni','U','AlpUni','N','Num','D','Date','T','Time','L','Logical','') & IF (LastPark(0)='' OR InStr(LastPark(0),'From')>0,'From','') & IF (InStr(LastPark(0),'To')>0,'To','') & IF ({0,12} AND ({0,16}='A' OR {0,16}='U' OR {0,16}='N'),'Combo','') ,0,0)
